    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>游戏简介</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2112200/extras/bb450305f76201cd357c51f0ece2d679.poster.avif?t=1749636325\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2112200/extras/bb450305f76201cd357c51f0ece2d679.webm?t=1749636325\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2112200/extras/bb450305f76201cd357c51f0ece2d679.mp4?t=1749636325\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>在一片荒芜黑暗的大陆上，一场宏大残酷的生存竞技揭开了帷幕， 只有战胜重重怪物，你才能笑到最后，成为竞技场的王者！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>游戏玩法</strong></h2><strong>※选择你最喜欢的英雄展开战斗</strong><br>解锁10名拥有不同特性的传奇英雄，选择你最喜爱的一个在紧张刺激的竞技场中大展身手吧！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2112200/extras/803f462d6ad9015249cf4e32a9296509.poster.avif?t=1749636325\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2112200/extras/803f462d6ad9015249cf4e32a9296509.webm?t=1749636325\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2112200/extras/803f462d6ad9015249cf4e32a9296509.mp4?t=1749636325\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>※在海量敌人中生存下来</strong><br>击败不断逼近的敌人以变强升级，通过搭配升级时任选其一的随机技能，每把你都能体验不同技能组合碰撞出的激烈化学反应，形成全新的战斗风格！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2112200/extras/00b2fdc223331a1f969cdbf77dcc2031.poster.avif?t=1749636325\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2112200/extras/00b2fdc223331a1f969cdbf77dcc2031.webm?t=1749636325\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2112200/extras/00b2fdc223331a1f969cdbf77dcc2031.mp4?t=1749636325\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>※在海量敌人中穿插游走</strong><br>通过精妙的走位在海量敌人的间隙中不停穿插游走，每一步都走得惊心动魄，收获在危险边缘疯狂试探的刺激快感！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2112200/extras/0a59689cf1a447358e8e48c034b8eed9.poster.avif?t=1749636325\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2112200/extras/0a59689cf1a447358e8e48c034b8eed9.webm?t=1749636325\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2112200/extras/0a59689cf1a447358e8e48c034b8eed9.mp4?t=1749636325\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>※高风险高回报的BOSS等你挑战</strong><br>击败随机刷新的强大BOSS，获得额外能力提升回报，让你接下来的割草体验更加如鱼得水！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2112200/extras/95ce8f928b0036defead6529e3aacfa3.poster.avif?t=1749636325\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2112200/extras/95ce8f928b0036defead6529e3aacfa3.webm?t=1749636325\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2112200/extras/95ce8f928b0036defead6529e3aacfa3.mp4?t=1749636325\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>※利用狂怒模式扭转局势</strong><br>总共拥有8种狂怒模式，灵活运用狂怒技能即可瞬间扭转战场上的局势，获得割草般的爽快体验。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2112200/extras/e31544916bbe06409aec0df8220e77ae.poster.avif?t=1749636325\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2112200/extras/e31544916bbe06409aec0df8220e77ae.webm?t=1749636325\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2112200/extras/e31544916bbe06409aec0df8220e77ae.mp4?t=1749636325\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>制作人员</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>制作人：安格法</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>游戏故事：安格法</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>策划：安格法</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>程序：安格法</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>美术：安格法</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>插画：安格法</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>UI：安格法</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>特效处理：安格法</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>音效处理：安格法</li></ul>",
